                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4122" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0569</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8315 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“投机”不成反蚀米:龙薇传媒并购万家文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Speculation&quot; does not become but be punished: Longwei Media acquires Wanjia Culture</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马杰，张钰卿</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东华理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙薇传媒，万家文化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高杠杆并购；并购程序；融资方式；并购风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">high leverage mergers and acquisitions; merger and acquisition procedures; financing methods; merger risk;</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着并购的发展，杠杆并购在金融市场上的比重越来越高，隐藏的风险也随之暴露。本案例描述了龙薇传媒高杠杆并购万家文化的详细过程。并购方实际控制人是“女版巴菲特”引来广泛关注；而后因融资不到位，龙薇传媒变更减持协议；并且在并购期间万家文化被证监会调查；最后并购宣布失败。然而并购事件还未结束，万家文化和赵薇均被证监会予以行政处罚、上海证券交易所予以纪律处分、被浙江省人民法院判赔偿。并购的失败让我们认识到并购应选择合理的并购杠杆比例、进行合法的并购程序、采用合适的融资方式以及警惕各并购阶段潜在的财务风险。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the development of mergers and acquisitions（ M&amp;A）, the proportion of leveraged mergers and acquisitions in the financial market is increasing , and the hidden risks are also exposed. This case describes the detailed process of Longwei Media&#39;s highly leveraged acquisition of Wanjia culture. The actual controller of the M&amp;A party was “female version of Buffett” which attracted extensive attention; then, due to the lack of financing, Longwei Media changed the reduction agreement, and Wanjia Culture was investigated by the Securities and Futures Commission during the merger; the final merger failed. However, the M&amp;A event has not yet ended. Wanjia Culture and Zhao Wei were all given administrative penalties by the CSRC, disciplinary action by the Shanghai Stock Exchange, and compensation by the Zhejiang Provincial People&#39;s Court.The failure of M&amp;A let us know that M&amp;A should choose reasonable leverage ratios, conduct legal mergers and acquisitions, adopt appropriate financing methods, and be alert to potential financial risks in each stage of M&amp;A.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计》、《公司财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
